nodes.text: Docking bay 789012634 was a docking bay located on level 3301 of Byblos tower 214. Some time during the Galactic Civil War, the smuggler Crimson was arrested here by Imperial Customs. Shortly after her arrest, she managed to escape with the help of her protocol droid U-THR and drama once more took place in the docking bay, as she and the droid sabotaged the blast doors and made off in the Starlight Red.
